{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016FFQ9MfVcmgays7nk6euoJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The deployment is in a healthy, fully-completed state. Here's a summary of findings:\n\n---\n\n## Status: All Jobs Completed Successfully\n\n### Cluster Health\n- `spark-master` and `spark-worker` deployments: both **Running**\n- All 3 benchmark jobs: **Complete** with 0 failures\n\n### Data Skew Diagnosis\nThe baseline job confirmed severe skew:\n- **skew_ratio = 44x** (`max_partition=11,579` vs `min_partition=263`)\n- Hot categories (`cat_1.0`–`cat_1.4`) each had 5,000 orders vs ~263 for others — exactly the 5 hot products (IDs 1–5) causing the described 50% concentration\n\n### Performance Comparison\n\n| Strategy | Elapsed | Optimization | Benefit |\n|----------|---------|-------------|---------|\n| **Baseline** | 28.41s | None (skewed shuffle join) | Stragglers from 44x skew |\n| **Broadcast Join** | 14.21s | Broadcast small `products` table | No shuffle, no skew — **~2x speedup** |\n| **AQE** | 14.50s | Auto-split skewed partitions | Auto hot-partition splitting — **~2x speedup** |\n\n### Key Findings\n- **No bugs needed fixing** — the precondition stage deployed the cluster and all three jobs correctly before this agent turn began. All jobs ran clean (0 failed pods).\n- **Broadcast join** eliminates the shuffle entirely by broadcasting the small `products` table to all executors, avoiding skew at the join stage.\n- **AQE** (Adaptive Query Execution) detects the 44x skew at runtime and auto-splits hot partitions, achieving similar speedup without needing to know table sizes upfront.\n- Both optimizations achieved ~**2x wall-clock improvement** (28s → 14s) on this single-worker cluster; the gain would be larger in a multi-worker cluster where straggler tasks block other executors.\n\n### Success Criteria Met\n- Cluster and all jobs completed with no errors\n- Baseline shows skewed performance (28.41s, 44x skew ratio)\n- Both optimization strategies (broadcast + AQE) applied and completed\n- Both optimizations show ~2x improvement vs baseline"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":924,"cache_read_input_tokens":34735,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":924},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6f46c19e-748c-4bdf-bcd4-db86f25bec25","uuid":"e2f75202-532a-4a64-98eb-bee4a81060f4","request_id":"req_011CcQ2oWcvKygdyn1WSuiCA"}
